{"tid":1114843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3南亞青年闖路軌狂奔　與輕鐵競速","createTime":"2019-04-18T17:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T01:31:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6041e70e6a5a6d8cd7dfa420c615b6fb808d4632","tid":1114843,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2698210/org/d9590f09f186b32717a009c4c3914d24.jpg/LtB3kJYCVQCUkvFJiUrARo415JJ3ydxFvtbNl77WzZc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2698210%2Forg%2Fd9590f09f186b32717a009c4c3914d24.jpg%2FLtB3kJYCVQCUkvFJiUrARo415JJ3ydxFvtbNl77WzZc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d90fa442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貪玩到闖入路軌玩命？元朗有數名南亞青年趁輕鐵行駛時，多番衝到路軌上狂奔。片段傳開後，大批網民狂派嬲。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「要求遣返難民大聯盟」於周三（17日）上傳片段，只見在輕鐵元朗總站對開位置，有3名南亞裔男子在馬路旁邊等候，待輕鐵駛近時，跑上路軌與輕鐵競速。<br />\n<br />\n雖然車長多次響號，但3名男子亦選擇無視，滿臉笑容地在路軌上奔跑，又不時傳出笑聲。當跑約幾十米後，有人跑回馬路閃避，有人則跑至燈位附近，會合持機拍攝的同伴。據片段所示，他們至少在3架列車前奔跑。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評︰「車死唔抵可憐」、「低能定弱智？玩咩唔好，要拎自己條命去玩」、「黐黐哋」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《香港鐵路（西北鐵路）附例》，任何人不得進入或登上鐵路處所的任何部分，但藉告示、指示牌和其他指示而清楚界定供使用鐵路的人使用的部分除外，也不得使用指定的入口或出口以外的地點進入或離開該等部分。一經定罪，可被罰款5000港元。"},{"pid":"ae38e2c19377d516de81d45158d20cd0366044b1","tid":1114843,"uid":225760,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ecb1963eb42d64af659b3d6d998286ce0544d7d","tid":1114843,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9547781699381168a7b77d8c860070cfdf321622","tid":1114843,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"又係呢班垃圾"},{"pid":"1698b4bcef9320a989f4b617bb83cb7cb7db113a","tid":1114843,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54394a4249a5ce5b93bee25532760f9303646410","tid":1114843,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"片 <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418124501335-0418_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR13nRZWud0vNAcDZH9q5b43Yg5cFVwTkWTwQLDJUa6Z0dM5Yu_i10d7BN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190418%2Fbkn-20190418124501335-0418_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR13nRZWud0vNAcDZH9q5b43Yg5cFVwTkWTwQLDJUa6Z0dM5Yu_i10d7BN8&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=0304f4d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190418/bkn-20190418124501335-0418_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR13nRZWud0vNAcDZH9q5b43Yg5cFVwTkWTwQLDJUa6Z0dM5Yu_i10d7BN8</a>"}]}